---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Builder Margin and Markup Calculator"
  description="Calculate builder margin, markup, and total cost including GST. Understand the difference between margin and markup when dealing with builders."
>
  <div class="breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; <a href="/inclusions/">Inclusions &amp; Options</a> &rsaquo; <span>Builder Margin &amp; Markup</span>
  </div>

  <h1>Builder Margin and Markup Calculator</h1>

  <button
    id="page-like-btn"
    class="like-btn"
    data-slug="builder-margin-and-markup"
    aria-label="Like this page"
  >
    <span class="like-heart">&#9829;</span>
    <span class="like-count">–</span>
  </button>

  <p>A common source of confusion when dealing with builders is the difference between <strong>margin</strong> and <strong>markup</strong>. These terms are not interchangeable.</p>

  <blockquote>
    <strong>A margin of 20% is NOT the same as a markup of 20%.</strong><br />
    A margin of 20% is equivalent to a markup of 25%.
  </blockquote>

  <h2>Understanding the Difference</h2>

  <p><strong>Markup</strong> is calculated on the cost price:<br />
  Cost + (Cost × markup%) = Sale price</p>

  <p><strong>Margin</strong> is calculated on the sale price:<br />
  Cost ÷ (1 − margin%) = Sale price (ex. GST)</p>

  <div style="display:flex;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:20px 0">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:220px">
      <p><strong>To calculate what the builder will charge</strong></p>
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Cost ex GST</td><td>$1,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Margin</td><td>20%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total with margin</td><td>$1,250 (cost/(1-0.2))</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total with margin &amp; GST</td><td>$1,375 (above × 1.1)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:220px">
      <p><strong>To calculate cost price from builders charge</strong></p>
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Builders variation</td><td>$1,375</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Margin</td><td>20%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total without GST</td><td>$1,250 (variation/1.1)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total cost</td><td>$1,000 (above×(1-0.2))</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>To easily calculate this, you can use a factor of 1.375, including GST. $1,000 * 1.375 = $1,375</p>

  <h2>Cost incl. Builder Margin Calculator</h2>

  <div class="calculator-card" id="calc1">
    <div class="calc-row">
      <label for="c1-cost">Cost ex. GST</label>
      <div class="input-group">
        <span class="prefix">$</span>
        <input type="number" id="c1-cost" value="1000" min="0" step="0.01" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="calc-row">
      <label for="c1-margin">Builder Margin % (not markup)</label>
      <div class="input-group">
        <input type="number" id="c1-margin" value="20" min="0" max="99" step="0.1" />
        <span class="suffix">%</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button class="calc-btn" id="c1-btn">Calculate</button>

    <div class="calc-results" id="c1-results">
      <div class="result-row">
        <span>Markup</span>
        <strong id="c1-markup"></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="result-row">
        <span>Total cost to client (ex. GST)</span>
        <strong id="c1-total-ex"></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="result-row highlight">
        <span>Total cost to client (incl. GST)</span>
        <strong id="c1-total-incl"></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="result-row">
        <span>Additional cost (incl. GST)</span>
        <strong id="c1-additional"></strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Cost before Builder Margin Calculator</h2>

  <div class="calculator-card" id="calc2">
    <div class="calc-row">
      <label for="c2-total">Total cost incl. builder margin and GST</label>
      <div class="input-group">
        <span class="prefix">$</span>
        <input type="number" id="c2-total" value="1375" min="0" step="0.01" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="calc-row">
      <label for="c2-margin">Builder Margin % (not markup)</label>
      <div class="input-group">
        <input type="number" id="c2-margin" value="20" min="0" max="99" step="0.1" />
        <span class="suffix">%</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button class="calc-btn" id="c2-btn">Calculate</button>

    <div class="calc-results" id="c2-results">
      <div class="result-row">
        <span>Markup</span>
        <strong id="c2-markup"></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="result-row highlight">
        <span>Cost before margin and GST</span>
        <strong id="c2-cost"></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="result-row">
        <span>Builder's Margin Amount</span>
        <strong id="c2-margin-amount"></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="result-row">
        <span>GST Component</span>
        <strong id="c2-gst"></strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Common Margin Multipliers (incl. 10% GST)</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Margin %</th>
        <th>Markup %</th>
        <th>Multiplier (incl. GST)</th>
        <th>Example: $10,000 cost</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>10%</td><td>11.1%</td><td>×1.222</td><td>$12,222</td></tr>
      <tr><td>15%</td><td>17.6%</td><td>×1.294</td><td>$12,941</td></tr>
      <tr><td>20%</td><td>25.0%</td><td>×1.375</td><td>$13,750</td></tr>
      <tr><td>25%</td><td>33.3%</td><td>×1.467</td><td>$14,667</td></tr>
      <tr><td>30%</td><td>42.9%</td><td>×1.571</td><td>$15,714</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

</Layout>

<style>
  blockquote {
    background: #f0f7fb;
    border-left: 4px solid #0073aa;
    padding: 15px 20px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .calculator-card {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin: 20px 0 30px;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .calc-row {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .calc-row label {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .input-group {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .input-group input {
    flex: 1;
    border: none;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    outline: none;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .prefix, .suffix {
    padding: 9px 12px;
    background: #eee;
    color: #555;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .calc-btn {
    background: #0073aa;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .calc-btn:hover {
    background: #005177;
  }

  .calc-results {
    margin-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding-top: 16px;
  }

  .result-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 7px 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .result-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .result-row.highlight {
    background: #e8f4f8;
    padding: 7px 10px;
    margin: 4px -10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border-bottom: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .result-row strong {
    color: #0073aa;
  }

  .result-row.highlight strong {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #005177;
  }
</style>

<script>
  function formatCurrency(value: number): string {
    return '$' + value.toFixed(2).replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ',');
  }

  function formatPercent(value: number): string {
    return value.toFixed(2) + '%';
  }

  function calc1() {
    const cost = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c1-cost') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    const margin = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c1-margin') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    if (isNaN(cost) || isNaN(margin) || margin >= 100 || margin < 0) return;
    const totalExGST = cost / (1 - margin / 100);
    const totalInclGST = totalExGST * 1.1;
    const additional = totalInclGST - cost;
    const markup = (totalExGST / cost - 1) * 100;
    (document.getElementById('c1-markup') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatPercent(markup);
    (document.getElementById('c1-total-ex') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatCurrency(totalExGST);
    (document.getElementById('c1-total-incl') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatCurrency(totalInclGST);
    (document.getElementById('c1-additional') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatCurrency(additional);
  }

  function calc2() {
    const total = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c2-total') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    const margin = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c2-margin') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    if (isNaN(total) || isNaN(margin) || margin >= 100 || margin < 0) return;
    const totalExGST = total / 1.1;
    const cost = totalExGST * (1 - margin / 100);
    const marginAmount = totalExGST - cost;
    const gst = total - totalExGST;
    const markup = (totalExGST / cost - 1) * 100;
    (document.getElementById('c2-markup') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatPercent(markup);
    (document.getElementById('c2-cost') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatCurrency(cost);
    (document.getElementById('c2-margin-amount') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatCurrency(marginAmount);
    (document.getElementById('c2-gst') as HTMLElement).textContent = formatCurrency(gst);
  }

  // Auto-calculate on load with default values
  calc1();
  calc2();

  document.getElementById('c1-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const cost = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c1-cost') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    const margin = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c1-margin') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    if (isNaN(cost) || isNaN(margin) || margin >= 100 || margin < 0) {
      alert('Please enter valid values. Margin must be between 0 and 99.');
      return;
    }
    calc1();
  });

  document.getElementById('c2-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const total = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c2-total') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    const margin = parseFloat((document.getElementById('c2-margin') as HTMLInputElement).value);
    if (isNaN(total) || isNaN(margin) || margin >= 100 || margin < 0) {
      alert('Please enter valid values. Margin must be between 0 and 99.');
      return;
    }
    calc2();
  });

  // Allow Enter key to trigger calculation
  document.querySelectorAll('.calculator-card input').forEach(input => {
    input.addEventListener('keypress', (e: Event) => {
      if ((e as KeyboardEvent).key === 'Enter') {
        const card = (e.target as HTMLElement).closest('.calculator-card');
        const btn = card?.querySelector('.calc-btn') as HTMLButtonElement;
        btn?.click();
      }
    });
  });

  // Like button
  const likeBtn = document.getElementById('page-like-btn') as HTMLButtonElement | null;
  if (likeBtn) {
    const slug = likeBtn.dataset.slug!;
    const countEl = likeBtn.querySelector('.like-count') as HTMLElement;
    let hasLiked = false;
    fetch(`/api/likes/${slug}`)
      .then(r => r.json())
      .then(({ count }: { count: number }) => { countEl.textContent = String(count); })
      .catch(() => { countEl.textContent = '0'; });
    likeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (hasLiked) return;
      hasLiked = true;
      const current = parseInt(countEl.textContent || '0');
      countEl.textContent = String(current + 1);
      likeBtn.classList.add('liked');
      fetch(`/api/likes/${slug}`, { method: 'POST' })
        .then(r => r.json())
        .then(({ count }: { count: number }) => {
          if (count > parseInt(countEl.textContent || '0')) countEl.textContent = String(count);
        })
        .catch(() => {});
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  .like-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    background: #f7f7f7;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 7px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #888;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .like-btn:hover { border-color: #bbb; background: #efefef; }
  .like-btn.liked .like-heart { color: #e53935; }
  .like-heart { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1; color: #e53935; }
</style>
